<bibRefCitation id="EFB807CC04521501FD1048B8FCA4F958" author="Albano, P. G. &amp; Bakker, P. A. J." box="[563,847,1681,1708]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="33 - 78" refId="ref141725" refString="Albano, P. G. &amp; Bakker, P. A. J. (2016) Annotated catalogue of the types of Triphoridae (Mollusca, Gastropoda) in the Museum fur Naturkunde, Berlin, with lectotype designations. Zoosystematics and Evolution, 92 (1), 33 - 78. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zse. 92.5936" type="journal article" year="2016">Albano &amp; Bakker (2016)</bibRefCitation>
